causal_map:
Boundary condition transformation → g(u); 
  g(u) → Solution u(x, y, t); 
  Solution u(x, y, t) → Laplace equation; 
  Laplace equation → Natural evolution of the system; 
  Natural evolution of the system → Solution u(x, y, t) at t = T; 
  Solution u(x, y, t) at t = T → Difference from original solution; 
  Difference from original solution → Impact on the system
